snippet.title: Starbase Ship Showcase | Ep. 2
snippet.description:
Some new crazy ships we have this week:


- Black3's "Brontes" (Battle Cruiser and Mining Versions)
- F.A.T. Ltd.'s "KOIOS Transferens Mk2-5S1G3W80c+" Mining/Utility Ship
- Senkii's Personal DeLorean-like Hovercraft


Contact FatFly#6857 on Discord to talk about his company or to purchase this fantastic craft.
Check out Senkii's Twitch channel at twitch.com/senk_ii to see more of his live Starbase content!
